## CODING RULES
- All agents have homeworld_serial = their physical silicon serial
  M5 agents → "GTH4921YP3"
  M1 agents → "C07FL0JAQ6NV"
- NEVER mix these. An agent born on M1 must not have an M5 serial.
- All financial ledger events must be Ed25519 signed via System/crypto_keychain.py
  Use sign_block() from System/crypto_keychain — never bare SHA256 for seals
- STGM is the internal economy token. Never mint tokens without a signed ledger entry.
- Dead drop = m5queen_dead_drop.jsonl — this is the Swarm chat log. Append only.
- human_signals.jsonl is the inference task queue. Write MINE_INFERENCE payloads here.

